hopobject.body: I'd like to speak to someone about a mortgage pharmerz.com But there are hot women on the street too? There might be a hot woman in your car, or on your dashboard display? I guess what I’m saying is that anything “can” be a distraction, but that doesn’t mean we should create laws banning everything. It hasn’t proven to cause accidents yet and it’s certainly much much better than any phone that has ever existed in almost every way. And it stays out of your way and off most of the time.
